pounding on him made my day. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Evidently it got their attention.  When they attacked our camp about 5 minutes later with about double our forces, I seemed to be their primary initial target.  I didn't last long at all with a mage epic pet, BL warder, spectre pet, a couple of skellies, etc all pounding on me. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
As for normal use for the spell... I would consider memming it for emergencies in The Hole or maybe some of the new PoP zones where there are a lot of summoned beings. <p><table border="0" width="100%">
